The paper discusses the development and deployment of applications in Cloud computing environments, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). It also discusses Platform as a Service (PaaS), which is a subcategory of Cloud Computing (cs.CC). The paper also mentions the use of various technologies and platforms for Cloud computing, which falls under the categories of Software Engineering (cs.SE), Distributed Systems (cs.Distributed), and Programming Languages (cs.PL).
